ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我比人飛 被飛通常希望翻轉頭</blockquote><br />\n其實分開得一定有啲問題<br />\n再勉強一齊返對大家都冇好處</blockquote><br />\n所以都只係幻想 冇搵冇睇冇問冇傾</blockquote><br />\nKeep住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50175d1e1d2868c466fee492beed9305dcdf8439","tid":98844,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉 邊個唔係咁<br />\n拍多左幾次都唔及佢咁深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係覺得根本呢個世上唔會再有人好似佢咁對我<br />\n容忍晒我所有野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分咗5年手有時都依然會好似樓主咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係當你遇到一個Mr/Mrs Right嘅時候自然你就會放低以前嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n太寂寞先會掛住唔要你嘅人，佢唔值得你去眷戀<br />\n唔好再咁自卑啦，佢唔係真係你諗到咁好，你要俾d信心自己終有一日你可以比以前更幸褔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1937f9a60ab85a2866375c9192f8d70ed72468b1","tid":98844,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>初戀係難忘架啦<br />\nbtw, 拍過好多次拖真係好仔極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但就係咁<br />\n我先覺得點解佢可以忍我咁耐<br />\n之前每一次拍拖都一年內<br />\n同我over八年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地而家幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n散果時我27佢32<br />\n而家過左兩年幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開波以為你地小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d可惜喎，應該都到左談婚論嫁嘅地步<br />\n如果佢搵返你，你會唔會同佢從新開始"},{"pid":"98ad73c50fbcb517413229d7bef4d774b72fef99","tid":98844,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打分手之後仲有無搵過佢？</blockquote><br />\n冇呀<br />\n一啲佢既野都唔知</blockquote><br />\n我整走哂佢啲野就係唔想再諗起佢<br />\n原來愛一個人真係可以由愛到恨再懷念<br />\n總之好覆雜<br />\n做過每樣野都同佢有關"},{"pid":"13e23e412513c3ebe4fd932bbc713cdcf1b53fe7","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地而家幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n散果時我27佢32<br />\n而家過左兩年幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開波以為你地小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d可惜喎，應該都到左談婚論嫁嘅地步<br />\n如果佢搵返你，你會唔會同佢從新開始</blockquote><br />\n小朋友點八年？十歲一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔算既，冇人講過要結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會喇，畢竟好清楚大家唔適合"},{"pid":"3ad4b465dc9f16368a9bb881b0a18da87663b7b2","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唉 邊個唔係咁<br />\n拍多左幾次都唔及佢咁深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係覺得根本呢個世上唔會再有人好似佢咁對我<br />\n容忍晒我所有野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分咗5年手有時都依然會好似樓主咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係當你遇到一個Mr/Mrs Right嘅時候自然你就會放低以前嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n太寂寞先會掛住唔要你嘅人，佢唔值得你去眷戀<br />\n唔好再咁自卑啦，佢唔係真係你諗到咁好，你要俾d信心自己終有一日你可以比以前更幸褔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇一世都唔會遇到"},{"pid":"a776f5e33bec485c5995f0723e82d677dd5230dd","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打分手之後仲有無搵過佢？</blockquote><br />\n冇呀<br />\n一啲佢既野都唔知</blockquote><br />\n我整走哂佢啲野就係唔想再諗起佢<br />\n原來愛一個人真係可以由愛到恨再懷念<br />\n總之好覆雜<br />\n做過每樣野都同佢有關</blockquote><br />\n我同佢基本上得電話呢樣聯絡方法<br />\n冇其他social media<br />\n冇common fd<br />\n所以分手之後除非主動直接搵<br />\n否則唔會知佢任何野"},{"pid":"c88e9ee5790d4958bb14bfcff4410d017134c00e","tid":98844,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地而家幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n散果時我27佢32<br />\n而家過左兩年幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開波以為你地小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d可惜喎，應該都到左談婚論嫁嘅地步<br />\n如果佢搵返你，你會唔會同佢從新開始</blockquote><br />\n小朋友點八年？十歲一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔算既，冇人講過要結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會喇，畢竟好清楚大家唔適合</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講8年之前，因為你話初戀所以我先入為主左你地係小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我覺得你唔應該成日凝住你唔會再拍拖或者唔會再有人對你咁好，咁樣就算有人想approach你都唔會有結果，試下放低身段去接受下一段感情咪仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7260065600c20eb418c414d8db18d0b1381b5fc8","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一開波以為你地小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d可惜喎，應該都到左談婚論嫁嘅地步<br />\n如果佢搵返你，你會唔會同佢從新開始</blockquote><br />\n小朋友點八年？十歲一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔算既，冇人講過要結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會喇，畢竟好清楚大家唔適合</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講8年之前，因為你話初戀所以我先入為主左你地係小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我覺得你唔應該成日凝住你唔會再拍拖或者唔會再有人對你咁好，咁樣就算有人想approach你都唔會有結果，試下放低身段去接受下一段感情咪仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我應該打到1999左<br />\n係同佢一齊左八年以上<br />\n散左兩年幾<br />\n<br />\n我圈子冇乜男<br />\n都試過上網識人<br />\n但好快覺得唔岩傾<br />\n可見既範圍內真係唔覺會有可能有下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e38981b89741a71ae39a901c4f770aa17786fa","tid":98844,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"我都想我ex會掛住我"},{"pid":"1a5a97ff6520e9f8264ce60a531819250d805b53","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想我ex會掛住我</blockquote><br />\n我成日諗佢會唔會結左婚生埋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eaa9d9746937727452bee3094c32b88e76ac807","tid":98844,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n但就係咁<br />\n我先覺得點解佢可以忍我咁耐<br />\n之前每一次拍拖都一年內<br />\n同我over八年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地而家幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n散果時我27佢32<br />\n而家過左兩年幾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該同絲打同年"},{"pid":"ff0b439feecf356693c89579d4543e1ae41486d6","tid":98844,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地而家幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n散果時我27佢32<br />\n而家過左兩年幾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該同絲打同年</blockquote><br />\n一把年紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385b011a6fcf36e92fc5510915183648c73dcf4d","tid":98844,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想我ex會掛住我</blockquote><br />\n我成日諗佢會唔會結左婚生埋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote